      "date": "2011-05-24 12:48:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nThe difference between patch set 2 and 1 is that we need avoid using do_rpc_nodes on the local node. This is because the init_test_env function called by rpc.sh would perform \"rm -f $TMP/*active\" during the failover testing and break the testing.\n\nHere is the test result with patch set 1:\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3f328296-854f-11e0-b4df-52540025f9af\n\nAnd here is the result with patch set 2:\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c52ed080-8602-11e0-b4df-52540025f9af",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
